  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nWould be possible to have a VS Code extension that allow me to launch tests via a configurable keyboard shortcut?\r\n\r\n- One shortcut to launch full test coverage\r\n- One shortcut to launch tests on the opened `.t.sol` file (run only tests inside the opened file)\r\n- One shortcut to launch test on the currently selected test function (the extension should see in which test my cursor is hover/have clicked into before)\r\n\r\nbonus be able to configure multiple shortcuts and specify additional parameters to launch the tests with (like the profile / custom env variables)\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
